ideas, thoughts and concept description on online advertisement 

Usefulness: In terms of using cellular data, as well as, loading webpages quickly using Wi-Fi, how much Internet data is used to load ads? 
It's striking that some ads are more heavy then others when it comes to data usage. 
Comparing interactive ads that give you the possibility to play games, watch a video or listen to sound with simple one-picture ads 

We're interested in how much of the data we use on our daily life is actually unwanted and therefore used for loading and screening ads. 

